description: Island inspired Sandwiches and tacos.What’s better than having a mobile kitchen show up to your event? It makes the possibilities endless. Our team of highly qualified professionals will make any event a pleasure. Fusion on the Run is your best choice for weddings and parties. Our attention to detail, experience, and reliability ensure that your event will be a smashing success.Our food reflects our commitment to exceptional quality. All meals are prepared with a passion for perfection. All of our meat is hormone free. Our food suppliers are the best in the business. Your guests will be talking about your wonderful food for days to come. Our menu has been developed over a three year period, with new dishes being added regularly.
name: Fusion on the Run
